{"tid":1935072,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"[麻雀妹親自教你填] 如何在您的美國人口普查表格上填寫「香港人」","createTime":"2020-03-20T10:09:00.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-22T09:11:03.000Z","uid":240362,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"a5c1a95ad58983aee84e9d3f537ebf04ea4eae9e","tid":1935072,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-20T10:09:00.000Z","msg":"SHARE哂俾你地美國親朋好友睇 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=tH165Wlxjc4\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DtH165Wlxjc4&d=YPVRFrdDXDTQtjhmChTpXMF4Sk7tP0df8nBEIt5zy0g%3D&h=968d526d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=tH165Wlxjc4</a><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">請支持我們未來兩個月的宣傳工作：<a href=\"https://www.gofundme.com/f/us-2020-census-write-in-hongkonger\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.gofundme.com%2Ff%2Fus-2020-census-write-in-hongkonger&d=YPVRFrdDXDTQtjhmChTpXMF4Sk7tP0df8nBEIt5zy0g%3D&h=9ea938d4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.gofundme.com/f/us-2020-census-write-in-hongkonger</a><br />\n<br />\n＊請記得填寫「香港人」，或英文全寫HONGKONGER，不須空格分隔，不要填「Hong Konger」或「Hong Kong」<br />\n- 不論您 國際學生抑或無文件移民，法律規定所有居住於美國境內的人均須參與普查<br />\n- 您 三種方法完成普查：網上、電話、問卷郵寄，填寫時將會有英文及中文版本可供選擇<br />\n- 請由現在至五月底前回應普查問卷<br />\n<br />\n&ndash;&ndash;&ndash;&ndash;&ndash;&ndash;&ndash;&ndash;&ndash;&ndash;&ndash;&ndash;&ndash;&ndash;&ndash;&ndash;&ndash;&ndash;&ndash;<br />\nFacebook: <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/wethehongkongers\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fwethehongkongers&d=YPVRFrdDXDTQtjhmChTpXMF4Sk7tP0df8nBEIt5zy0g%3D&h=9604a461\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/wethehongkongers</a><br />\nInstagram: <a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/wethehongkongers\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fwethehongkongers&d=YPVRFrdDXDTQtjhmChTpXMF4Sk7tP0df8nBEIt5zy0g%3D&h=c6fde608\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.instagram.com/wethehongkongers</a><br />\nTwitter: <a href=\"https://twitter.com/We_the_Hkers\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FWe_the_Hkers&d=YPVRFrdDXDTQtjhmChTpXMF4Sk7tP0df8nBEIt5zy0g%3D&h=51f061ca\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/We_the_Hkers</a><br />\nWebsite: <a href=\"https://www.wethehongkongers.org/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.wethehongkongers.org%2F&d=YPVRFrdDXDTQtjhmChTpXMF4Sk7tP0df8nBEIt5zy0g%3D&h=cae9a81d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.wethehongkongers.org/</a></span></strong>"},{"pid":"13fd2953fa0353061c7034ce9d34b303000d4ca1","tid":1935072,"uid":240362,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-20T10:09:27.000Z","msg":"Please support our campaign in the next two months and help us reach the goal on GoFundMe: <a href=\"https://www.gofundme.com/f/us-2020-census-write-in-hongkonger\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.gofundme.com%2Ff%2Fus-2020-census-write-in-hongkonger&d=YPVRFrdDXDTQtjhmChTpXMF4Sk7tP0df8nBEIt5zy0g%3D&h=9ea938d4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.gofundme.com/f/us-2020-census-write-in-hongkonger</a><br />\n<br />\n* Remember to write in 'HONGKONGER' in one word, not Hong Konger or Hong Kong. *<br />\n- Everyone living in the U.S., including international students and undocumented immigrants, is required by law to participate in the census.<br />\n- There are 3 ways you can fill out your form: online, by phone, and on the paper questionnaire. Both the English and Chinese languages are available.<br />\n- Respond to the census from now by the end of May."},{"pid":"9426ded6103ce8b20206321ff3f881fd15a16681","tid":1935072,"uid":240362,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-20T10:09:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"860ab9f63156a474992858991a8cf80e4e7e80e8","tid":1935072,"uid":240362,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-20T10:12:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2541637fc695beb810309113791fcaee9f1cddf3","tid":1935072,"uid":240362,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-20T10:14:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight_connect.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight_connect.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight_connect.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"49d27c2b373fc8631a63a78427a48a00200b7218","tid":1935072,"uid":240362,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-20T10:16:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" 